<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Poland" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Poland,</orth> country to the east of Germany: <bibl n="shak. mm 1.3.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 3, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 4, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.361" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 361</bibl>. Adjectively: <emph>a P. winter</emph> (i. e. a very long winter) <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.100" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 2, 100</bibl>.
